[1126.28914, "o", "\u001b[0;35m[DEPRECATION WARNING]: INJECT_FACTS_AS_VARS default to `True` is deprecated, top-level facts will not be auto injected after the change. This feature will be removed from ansible-core version 2.24.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;35mOrigin: /Users/dshp/Desktop/code/python/ansible/roles/docker/tasks/main.yml:30:11\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;35m\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;35m28 - name: Add Docker apt repository\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;35m29   apt_repository:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;35m30     repo: \"deb [arch={{ 'amd64' if ansible_architecture == 'x86_64' else 'arm64' }} signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/do...\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;35m             ^ column 11\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;35m\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;35mUse `ansible_facts[\"fact_name\"]` (no `ansible_` prefix) instead.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;35m\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;32mok: [public]\u001b[0m\r\n"]
